⎕IO←0

⍝ === Create DCF files containing all data types ===
⍝ J=0, C=1, Z=0 for clearest binary analysis

base←'D:\_Utenti\stf.APLITA\Source\Repos\DCFFiles\'

⍝ Helper to create a fresh file
∇ tn←CreateDCF name;file
  file←base,name
  :Trap 0
    ⎕FERASE file ⎕FTIE 0
  :Else
  :EndTrap
  tn←file ⎕FCREATE 0
  ⎕FPROPS tn 'J' 0
  ⎕FPROPS tn 'C' 1
  ⎕FPROPS tn 'Z' 0
∇

