⍝ Comp 4: Decimal128 scalar
savefr←⎕FR
:Trap 0
  ⎕FR←1287
  1.5 ⎕FAPPEND tn
  ⎕←'  Decimal128 scalar written'
  ⎕FR←savefr
:Else
  ⎕←'  Decimal128 scalar FAILED: ',⍕⎕DM
  ⎕FR←savefr
  0 ⎕FAPPEND tn
:EndTrap

⍝ Comp 5: Decimal128 vector
